layout.text:
Lucky No. 7 is a Dutch unisex kids brand for 0 - 8 years. Boys only, Girls allowed! Lucky No.7 stands for tough, rebellious; just a little bit!
With a wink at teen fashion, comfort and a sustainability awareness.
